<view class="page-shell">
  <app-navbar title="我的" left-arrow="{{false}}" />

  <view class="page-body page-body--with-tabbar">
    <view class="summary-banner">
      <view class="summary-title">{{user.name}}</view>
      <view class="summary-desc">ID {{user.id}} · {{user.community}}</view>
    </view>

    <view class="section card info-card">
      <view class="section-head">
        <view>
          <view class="section-title">我的房屋</view>
          <view class="section-subtitle">房屋、成员和认证拆成独立页处理</view>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view wx:for="{{houses}}" wx:key="id" class="record-card profile-house">
        <view class="record-row">
          <view>
            <view class="record-title">{{item.name}}</view>
            <view class="record-note">{{item.memberCount}} 位成员</view>
          </view>
          <t-tag theme="primary" variant="light">{{item.role}}</t-tag>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="action-row section">
        <navigator class="secondary-button nav-button" url="/pages/profile/bind/index">绑定新房</navigator>
        <navigator class="primary-button nav-button" url="/pages/profile/members/index">成员管理</navigator>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="section card info-card">
      <view class="section-title">账户中心</view>
      <t-cell-group>
        <t-cell
          title="身份认证"
          description="查看实名审核与提交材料"
          note="{{verification.status === 'verified' ? '已认证' : '待处理'}}"
          arrow="{{true}}"
          url="/pages/profile/verification/index"
          jump-type="navigateTo"
        />
        <t-cell
          title="代办授权"
          description="委托家属或代理人代办业务"
          note="授权协作"
          arrow="{{true}}"
          url="/pages/profile/agent/index"
          jump-type="navigateTo"
        />
        <t-cell
          title="设置"
          description="通知、隐私与账号偏好"
          note="个人设置"
          arrow="{{true}}"
          url="/pages/profile/settings/index"
          jump-type="navigateTo"
        />
      </t-cell-group>
    </view>

    <view class="section page-note page-note--warning">
      管理端和小程序的能力边界已经拆开了：住户侧只做查看、申请、授权、投票和服务办理，不承担后台维护型操作。
    </view>
  </view>

  <app-tabbar value="profile" />
</view>
